user_query: I'm a fitness enthusiast and I'm looking for a training plan for my upcoming marathon. Can you fetch me the activities between July 14, 2014, and July 24, 2014, from the 2PEAK.com Dynamic TRAINING PLANS API? Additionally, provide me with the fixtures for the 2020 season of rugby.

TaskList.description: Fetch training activities for the specified date range from the 2PEAK.com Dynamic TRAINING PLANS API.
Fetch the fixtures for the 2020 rugby season.
